                    oc:textContent "Distribute work efficiently across parallel workers to maximize throughput and minimize completion time." ] ;
            oc:hasSubsection [ a oc:Section ;
                    oc:hasContent [ a oc:CodeExample ;
                            oc:blockType "code_block" ;
                            oc:codeContent """What's the workload characteristic?

Uniform task times:
├── Known count → Static partitioning (equal chunks)
├── Streaming input → Round-robin distribution
└── Large items → Size-aware partitioning

Variable task times:
├── Predictable variance → Weighted distribution
├── Unpredictable → Dynamic scheduling / work stealing
└── Long-tail distribution → Work stealing + time limits

Resource constraints:
├── Memory-bound workers → Memory-aware assignment
├── Heterogeneous workers → Capability-based routing
└── Network costs → Locality-aware placement
""" ;
                            oc:codeLanguage "" ;
                            oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                            oc:sourceLocation "lines 20-37" ] ;
                    oc:sectionLevel 2 ;
                    oc:sectionOrder 2 ;
                    oc:sectionTitle "Load Balancing Decision Tree" ],
