    oc:appliesToContext "When designing any parallel workload distribution" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Avoid over-partitioning (too many small tasks), starvation (large tasks blocking queues), thundering herd (all workers wake simultaneously), hot spots (uneven key distribution), and convoy effects (workers waiting on shared resources)." ;
